properties.name: barCollapsingEnabled
properties.summary: Indicates if the web dialog should enable collapsing of the navigation bar and hiding of the bottom toolbar when the user scrolls web content. For iOS, this API is available on iOS 11 and later.

properties.name: barColor
properties.summary: The bar-color of the web dialog. For iOS, available on iOS 10 and later.

properties.name: dismissButtonStyle
properties.summary: The dismiss-button-style of the web dialog close button. For iOS, this API is available on iOS 11 and later.

properties.name: entersReaderIfAvailable
properties.summary: Indicates if the reader version of content should be shown automatically.

properties.name: intentFlags
properties.summary: Intent flags to be used for the Chrome Custom Tab, specified as a Bitwise-OR
